      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep-luster finish and absolutely no road rash or imperfections. The interior is in pristine condition, featuring supple, unscuffed leather and a cabin that still retains its original fresh scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by the dealership to ensure peak performance. Every feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist technology, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
